('Wes Metroka', 'Advisory Committee · Battalion Chief', 'CFD', 'wesley.metroka@chicoca.gov', '530-828-2141',
 'I''ve been in the fire service for 24 years and am currently a Battalion Chief with the Chico Fire Department. My career began with Cal Fire in the Shasta/Trinity Unit. After two seasons with the state, I took a position with my hometown Paradise Fire Department. After 8 years in Paradise, I made the move to Chico Fire. Peer Support is one of the greatest wellness resources a fire department can promote and support.',
